Bhai to baat aise hai Linux pr graphics.h file chaiye hogi tumhe
Bhen ki chutx college k computer mai bhi ni hoga kuch to tumhari help krne k liye bani hai ye file
Shant se BASH urf terminal khol lena and fir usme ye code copy paste kr dena :

"wget https://sourceforge.net/projects/libxbgi/files/xbgi_365-1_amd64.deb"

ye tha first code iske baad kuch kuch hoga wait krna fir jb wo ho jaye tb next code copy paste krna "

"sudo dpkg -i xbgi_365-1_amd64.deb"

iski bhen ka tandola ye bhi run kr do fir sax sux ek dum 
maza ajyega baaki codes hai hi baju mai 
KRO MAUZ APKE ABBU NE APKI MDT KI HAI CANTEEN SE KUCH KHILA DENA
